1. To make the docker env ready, go to the file location of docker-compose.yml and run below command
   docker-compose up -d
2. To close the environment run the below comand
    docker-compose down
3. if you want to know about other environment variables which you want to add in your env set up through docker-compose.yml then use below command
   docker image inspect <IMAGE_ID>

   
